<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<wps:ProcessDescriptions xml:lang="en" service="WPS" version="1.0.0" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.opengis.net/wps/1.0.0 http://schemas.opengis.net/wps/1.0.0/wpsAll.xsd" xmlns:wps="http://www.opengis.net/wps/1.0.0" xmlns:ows="http://www.opengis.net/ows/1.1" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
  <ProcessDescription wps:processVersion="1.0.0" statusSupported="true" storeSupported="true">
    <ows:Identifier>kopss:CA_ConditionalEvaluation</ows:Identifier>
    <ows:Title>CA_ConditionalEvaluation</ows:Title>
    <ows:Abstract>Performs a conditional if/else evaluation on each of the input cells of an input raster.</ows:Abstract>
    <DataInputs>
      <Input maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="1">
        <ows:Identifier>inputCoverage</ows:Identifier>
        <ows:Title>The input gridcoverage to be processed.</ows:Title>
        <ows:Abstract>The input gridcoverage to be processed</ows:Abstract>
        <ComplexData>
          <Default>
            <Format>
              <MimeType>application/arcgrid</MimeType>
            </Format>
          </Default>
          <Supported>
            <Format>
              <MimeType>application/arcgrid</MimeType>
            </Format>
            <Format>
              <MimeType>image/geotiff</MimeType>
            </Format>
            <Format>
              <MimeType>image/tiff</MimeType>
            </Format>
          </Supported>
        </ComplexData>
      </Input>
      <Input maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="1">
        <ows:Identifier>inputFilter</ows:Identifier>
        <ows:Title>Input filter encoding</ows:Title>
        <ows:Abstract>Filter Encoding: Filter의 공간조건을 사용하는 경우 “the_geom”을 shape 필드로, 속성조건을 사용하는 경우 “Value” 또는 “inputCoverage의 이름”을 속성필드로 사용</ows:Abstract>
        <ComplexData>
          <Default>
            <Format>
              <MimeType>text/xml; subtype=filter/1.0</MimeType>
            </Format>
          </Default>
          <Supported>
            <Format>
              <MimeType>text/xml; subtype=filter/1.0</MimeType>
            </Format>
            <Format>
              <MimeType>text/xml; subtype=filter/1.1</MimeType>
            </Format>
            <Format>
              <MimeType>text/plain; subtype=cql</MimeType>
            </Format>
          </Supported>
        </ComplexData>
      </Input>
      <Input maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="1">
        <ows:Identifier>trueValue</ows:Identifier>
        <ows:Title>Input true constant value</ows:Title>
        <ows:Abstract>조건이 참일 경우 계산될 정수형의 값(Default = 1)</ows:Abstract>
        <LiteralData>
          <ows:DataType>xs:int</ows:DataType>
          <ows:AnyValue />
        </LiteralData>
      </Input>
      <Input maxOccurs="1" minOccurs="0">
        <ows:Identifier>falseValue</ows:Identifier>
        <ows:Title>Input false constant value</ows:Title>
        <ows:Abstract>조건이 거짓일 경우 계산될 정수형의 값, 만약 값이 입력되지 않으면 NoData로 처리한다.</ows:Abstract>
        <LiteralData>
          <ows:DataType>xs:int</ows:DataType>
          <ows:AnyValue />
        </LiteralData>
      </Input>
    </DataInputs>
    <ProcessOutputs>
      <Output>
        <ows:Identifier>result</ows:Identifier>
        <ows:Title>Result</ows:Title>
        <ComplexOutput>
          <Default>
            <Format>
              <MimeType>application/arcgrid</MimeType>
            </Format>
          </Default>
          <Supported>
            <Format>
              <MimeType>application/arcgrid</MimeType>
            </Format>
            <Format>
              <MimeType>image/geotiff</MimeType>
            </Format>
            <Format>
              <MimeType>image/tiff</MimeType>
            </Format>
          </Supported>
        </ComplexOutput>
      </Output>
    </ProcessOutputs>
  </ProcessDescription>
</wps:ProcessDescriptions>